text: Da Möb is a Swedish-American-Canadian animated series, created by Magnus Carlsson, about three youngsters who form a rap band called Da Möb. They go on misadventures to try to get a record deal; however, they are untalented and they are fighting a losing battle to make it in the music business. It aired in the United States from 2001 to 2002 and in Sweden from 2002 to 2003. The name Da Möb comes from The Mob with a joke heavy metal umlaut. ==Voices== {| class="wikitable" |- !
